alluxio.master.file.meta

Class TempInodePathForChild

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.master.file.meta.LockedInodePath
      • alluxio.master.file.meta.MutableLockedInodePath
        • alluxio.master.file.meta.TempInodePathForChild
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public final class TempInodePathForChild
extends MutableLockedInodePath
    This class represents a temporary LockedInodePath, with a child component joined to the existing path. This LockedInodePath will not unlock the inodes on close. This is useful for being able to pass in a new child path based on an existing LockedInodePath, without having to re-traverse the inode tree, and re-acquire locks. This allows methods to operate on a child path component extending from an existing LockedInodePath.
